### Chats & Messaging API Tests
# Make sure to set the relevant variables for testing

@baseUrl = http://localhost:10000/api
@userToken = your_user_jwt_token_here
@chatId = your_chat_id_here

###
# 1. Get my chats
GET {{baseUrl}}/chats
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###
# 2. Get chat messages
GET {{baseUrl}}/chats/{{chatId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###
# 3. Send text message
POST {{baseUrl}}/chats/{{chatId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "content": "Hello! I am ready to meet up for the found item."
}

###
# 4. Send image message (Requires multipart/form-data upload via VSCode REST client or Postman)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chats/{{chatId}}/messages/image
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=MyAppBoundary

--MyAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"

Here is proof
--MyAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="proof.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./local-image.jpg
--MyAppBoundary--
